dcterms:description: The WEBQUESTIONSSP dataset contains full semantic parses for a subset of the questions from WEBQUESTIONS, consisting of 3,098 question-answer pairs for training and 1,639 for testing, collected using Google Suggest API and originally answered by Amazon Mechanical Turk workers.
